24
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:26,130
If you were to see it,

25
00:02:26,850 --> 00:02:29,670
what difference would it make now that it's done?

26
00:02:29,670 --> 00:02:31,520
The future...

27
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:34,880
