203
00:19:34,610 --> 00:19:36,170
Yes.

204
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:39,970
What drink? I said I'm working right now.

205
00:19:40,990 --> 00:19:44,310
Then I guess I'll have to drink alone.

206
